        <div class="inline-cta">
          <div class="cta-copy">
            <h4>Pick two platforms — let us post to both.</h4>
            <p>theStacc auto-publishes <strong>30 posts a month</strong> to GBP, Facebook, Instagram, LinkedIn, and X — with local-flavoured hooks and seasonal prompts built in. One subscription, $49/mo.</p>
