        <p>For a B2C national brand, social media is the marketing engine. For a local business, social is one of <em>three feeders</em> into one outcome: a customer calls your phone or walks into your store.</p>

        <p>Every local-friendly platform delivers customers in one of three ways:</p>

        <ol>
