          <li><strong>Recommendation surface</strong> — friends/neighbours mention you (Facebook, Nextdoor).</li>
          <li><strong>Demand creation</strong> — somebody sees your content, remembers you next time (Instagram, TikTok, LinkedIn).</li>
        </ol>

        <div class="callout callout-warn">
          <div class="callout-label">⚠️ The "5 platforms in burst, then nothing" trap</div>
          <p>The #1 mistake local owners make: <strong>spreading thin across 5+ platforms for 3 weeks, then giving up.</strong> An abandoned profile is worse than no profile — it signals to potential customers that the business is dormant. Pick two. Commit for 12 months. Schedule, do not improvise.</p>
        </div>

